				\usepackage{amssymb} 
				\usepackage{amsbsy}
				\usepackage{mathrsfs}
				\usepackage{upgreek}
				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$$R_0$$\end{document}) declines. An extensive analysis of treatment effects, interactions with saboteurs, and other social influences confirmed that increases in transmission rates (\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
